# EWP-002 — Implement PlatformApplicationPackage

**Engine:** VS08 – License, Subscription & Tenant Management Engine

**Milestone:** VS08A – Tenant Foundation

**Capability Contract:** CC-002 – PlatformApplicationPackage

**Status:** Approved for Implementation

---

# Objective

Implement the **PlatformApplicationPackage** aggregate exactly as defined by the approved CAP architecture.

A PlatformApplicationPackage represents an immutable, versioned deployment artifact for a PlatformApplication.

It is the unit that is installed into a Tenant Workspace.

The Runtime Engine executes PlatformApplicationPackages—not PlatformApplications.

